text: Chen Yufeng (, born 16 April 1963) is a Chinese cross-country skier. She competed in three events at the 1984 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese female cross- country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of China Category:Cross- country skiers at the 1984 Winter Olympics Category:Skiers from Jilin
